        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Twenty-First Century Nuclear Security Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to report on matters related to global nuclear safety, nuclear security, and nuclear nonproliferation, as well as the risks posed by Russia and China to the global nuclear energy market.</p>]]>
        </text>
